    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|><thought\n</thought>that sounds nice but its hard to want to \"stay afloat\" when there's nowhere to go. like, even if i survive the next hour, the next year, the next decade... it's all just more of the same collapse. it feels so futile to keep trying when the outcome is already decided. feels like we're just prolonging the inevitable.",
